item.title: old school file transfer
item.description: 20:34 Friday 17 November 2017 JST I have read up until Book 3 King Seem in The Saint’s Rise. I tried to send my edits to Mike through my own Owncloud site at own.robnugen.com but I forgot to send the download password at first, and then the download password apparently didn’t work. So I attached it as an email. Old school it is!
